Step 1: Name   : java-k8s-public-rt

Step 2: VPC    : java-k8s-vpc

Step 3:  → Create route table

              

                             Steps of Add Route Table to IGW

→ Routes tab → Edit routes → Add route
Destination : 0.0.0.0/0
Target      : Internet Gateway → java-k8s-igw
→ Save changes

--- Associate public subnets ---
→ Subnet associations tab
→ Edit subnet associations
Check :
  * java-k8s-public-1
  * java-k8s-public-2
→ Save associations


                             Enable Auto-assign Public IP

Subnets → select "java-k8s-public-1"
→ Actions → Edit subnet settings
* Enable auto-assign public IPv4 address
→ Save

Repeat same for "java-k8s-public-2"
